## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **tarlatamab Imdelltra 2024** = first FDA DLL3 + CD3 bispecific T-cell engager — SCLC second-line. DeLLphi-301 trial. DLL3 가 SCLC neuroendocrine 85%+ 발현 + normal tissue 미발현 selective target. quantum-VQE 의 DLL3xCD3 Fab geometry 직접 fit. Rova-T 2018-2019 failure 후 DLL3-target 부활.
2. **rovalpituzumab tesirine Rova-T failed 2018-2019** = DLL3 PBD ADC — first DLL3 ADC. cutaneous toxicity + efficacy modest → discontinued. paradigm lessons: linker chemistry + DLL3 specificity + payload selection. quantum-VQE 의 ADC linker stability + DLL3 binding affinity comparator.
3. **atezolizumab + carbo + etoposide IMpower133 2019** = first FDA IO + chemo 1L ES-SCLC. mOS 12.3 vs 10.3 (HR 0.70). "limited but first" SCLC IO breakthrough 30+ year stagnation 후.
4. **durvalumab + platinum + etoposide CASPIAN 2020** = second IO + chemo 1L ES-SCLC. cisplatin 또는 carboplatin choice. mOS 13.0 vs 10.3.
5. **lurbinectedin Zepzelca 2020** = first FDA new mechanism SCLC second-line — RNA pol II + alkylator dual. topotecan 24+ year monopoly 후 alternative. PM-1183 trabectedin analogue.
6. **PE (platinum + etoposide) 35+ year 1L 표준** = cisplatin (LS-SCLC) 또는 carboplatin (ES-SCLC) + etoposide. cytotoxic chemo backbone 변화 미미 — IO 추가 가 first paradigm shift.
7. **SCLC subtype SCLC-A/N/P/I (ASCL1/NEUROD1/POU2F3/INSM1) 2018+** = transcription factor-defined subtypes. ASCL1 = DLL3-high → tarlatamab fit. POU2F3 = tuft-cell variant → 만성 PARP/AURKA sensitivity. NEUROD1 = LSD1 sensitive. precision medicine 의 시작.
8. **DDR (AURKA + WEE1 + ATR + ATM) + IO synergy research** = SCLC RB1/TP53 universal loss → DDR vulnerability. alisertib + adavosertib + ceralasertib 가 IO 와 결합. wet-lab signal 있음 — Phase II 진행.
9. **brain metastasis 50%+ SCLC** = PCI prophylactic cranial irradiation 가 1L LS-SCLC 표준. cross-precision_radiation_onc. tarlatamab BBB cross + nanobot delivery research 진행.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, SCLC 임상 의미 한정.

